---
// Featured destination spotlight — full-width CTA like Click&Boat's Greece section
---

<section class="relative h-[360px] sm:h-[400px] overflow-hidden" aria-labelledby="spotlight-heading">
  <img
    src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1613395877344-13d4a8e0d49e?w=1920&q=80&auto=format"
    alt="Sailing in Greece"
    class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover"
    loading="lazy"
    decoding="async"
  />
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-black/70 via-black/40 to-transparent"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 flex items-center h-full">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 w-full">
      <div class="max-w-lg">
        <p class="text-primary-light text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Featured destination</p>
        <h2 id="spotlight-heading" class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white mb-3">
          Greece
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-white/80 mb-2 font-medium">The Mediterranean Paradise</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/70 mb-6 leading-relaxed max-w-md">
          Discover the Greek islands by boat. From the volcanic beauty of Santorini to the vibrant nightlife of Mykonos, explore crystal clear waters and ancient coastlines.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a
            href="/boat-rental/greece"
            class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 rounded-xl bg-white text-text font-bold text-sm hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors"
          >
            Discover Greece
            <svg class="ml-2 h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"/></svg>
          </a>
          <a
            href="/boat-rental?location=greece"
            class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 rounded-xl bg-white/15 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/25 text-white font-bold text-sm hover:bg-white/25 transition-colors"
          >
            Browse 1,240+ boats
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
